    <text>
        <body>
            <div xml:id="d.1">
                <head type="title">Miklós Oláh to a friend (Ghent, 19 August 1533)</head>
                <floatingText type="regesta">
                    <body>
                        <p xml:id="reg.p.1">He has never been as dear to him as he is now if he does
                            what he is asking him to do. He will forgive him his impertinence if he
                            remembers how much he loves him. He is asking him to do what Joannes is
                            asking.</p>
                    </body>
                </floatingText>
                <pb facs="https://www.eleveltar.hu/kereso-portlet/spring/digitalcontent/getcontent/preservica/0F5D9C04-182C-4C37-9F44-C6DEB7961A1B
                    "/>
                <p xml:id="p.1">Nicolai Olai ad amicum.</p>
                <p xml:id="p.2">Quid queris? Impudensne tibi videor, quod id a te petam, cuius tu
                    quoque in magno sis desiderio, an perquam humanus, qui ea, quae tibi sunt
                    carissima, mihi dari exoptem. Tuum est iudicium aestimare, quem me esse
                    arbitreris, humanumne, an impudentem, verum hoc scito nunquam te mihi in re
                    aliqua </p>
                <pb facs="https://www.eleveltar.hu/kereso-portlet/spring/digitalcontent/getcontent/preservica/767B7A79-56D7-40A0-9CBD-7046034C408B
                    "/>
                <p xml:id="p.3">gratiorem praestitisse, quam nunc praestabis, si meae voluntati ex
                    animi mei sententia satisfeceris. Iam ne videor tibi omnino impudens, qui tam
                    fidenter a te hoc efflagitem? Nimirum desines mirari meam αἰσχύνην,<note
                        xml:id="note.1">‘my impudence’.</note> si cogitaris meum in te amorem, qui
                    usque adeo magnus est, ut impune me faciat inverecundum. Quare, mi Frater, <add
                        corresp="Olahus" type="insert">si</add> una hac <add corresp="Olahus"
                        type="insert">in</add> re, quam nunc peto, quamquam tibi
                        <persName>Ioannes</persName><note xml:id="note.2">Probably János
                        Czeglédi.</note> referet, mihi morem gesseris, nihil te unquam mei causa
                    negasse existimabo. Vale, τῶν φίλων ἀγαθώτατε καὶ <choice>
                        <orig>ἐμου</orig>
                        <supplied>ἐμοῦ</supplied>
                    </choice> φίλε.<note xml:id="note.3">‘my dear brilliant friend’.</note></p>
                <p xml:id="p.4"><placeName>Gandavi</placeName> 19. Augusti 1533.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
